qeantitative aptitude_programming-1 (1).doc - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. 1. The document contains 38 quantitative aptitude questions with multiple choice answers. 
2. The questions cover topics like numbers, divisibility, logarithms, ratios, and permutations & combinations.  
3. The goal is to solve the questions and select the correct answer from the options provided.
